{
  "permissions": {
    "allow": [
      "Read",
      "Write",
      "Edit",
      "Bash(ls *)",
      "Bash(find *)",
      "Bash(grep *)",
      "Bash(cat *)",
      "Bash(head *)",
      "Bash(tail *)",
      "Bash(wc *)",
      "Bash(echo *)",
      "Bash(pwd)",
      "Bash(diff *)",
      "Bash(jq *)",
      "Bash(mkdir *)",
      "Bash(mv *)",
      "Bash(cp *)",
      "Bash(chmod *)",
      "Bash(python *)",
      "Bash(python3 *)",
      "Bash(pip *)",
      "Bash(pip3 *)",
      "Bash({{PY}} .project_manager/tools/board.py *)",
      "Bash({{PY}} .project_manager/tools/pm_bootstrap.py *)",
      "Bash({{PY}} .project_manager/tools/pm_handoff.py *)",
      "Bash({{PY}} .project_manager/tools/ticket_finish.py *)",
      "Bash(CLAUDE_SESSION_NAME=pm {{PY}} .project_manager/tools/board.py *)",
      "Bash(CLAUDE_SESSION_NAME=pm {{PY}} .project_manager/tools/pm_bootstrap.py *)",
      "Bash(CLAUDE_SESSION_NAME=pm {{PY}} .project_manager/tools/pm_handoff.py *)",
      "Bash(CLAUDE_SESSION_NAME=pm {{PY}} .project_manager/tools/ticket_finish.py *)",
      "Bash(git status)",
      "Bash(git status *)",
      "Bash(git log *)",
      "Bash(git diff *)",
      "Bash(git add *)",
      "Bash(git commit *)",
      "Bash(git branch *)",
      "Bash(git checkout *)",
      "Bash(git mv *)",
      "Bash(git rm *)",
      "Bash({{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.claude/run_tests_hook.sh)",
      "Bash(gh auth *)",
      "Bash(git config *)",
      "Bash(ssh -T git@github.com)",
      "Bash(git init *)",
      "Bash(ssh-keyscan -t ed25519 github.com)",
      "Bash(ssh-keygen -lf -)",
      "Bash(mkdir -p ~/.ssh)",
      "Bash(git ls-remote *)",
      "Bash(git remote *)",
      "Bash(git push *)"
    ],
    "deny": [
      "Bash(rm -rf *)",
      "Bash(git push --force *)",
      "Bash(git push -f *)",
      "Bash(git reset --hard *)",
      "Bash(git clean -f *)"
    ]
  },
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.claude/run_tests_hook.sh",
            "timeout": 60,
            "statusMessage": "Running tests..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PreCompact": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "{{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.claude/precompact_capture_hook.sh",
            "timeout": 30
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "_comment": "Claude Code 프로젝트 공통 settings (git tracked·다른 PC/프로젝트 import 용). {{PROJECT_ROOT}} / {{PY}} 치환 필수. permissions.allow 는 보수적 기본값 — 프로젝트가 자주 쓰는 명령을 추가하라. PostToolUse hook 을 쓰지 않으려면 hooks 블록을 삭제. 로컬 머신 전용 권한 (harness 세션 중 자동 누적분 포함) 은 별도 settings.local.json (gitignore) 으로 분리."
}
